{"tid":832165,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求公平的定義","createTime":"2018-09-22T14:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T11:11:10.000Z","uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16cefd77ea3b8cb20210e539711f24e66132a846","tid":832165,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"其實公平係社會同成個世界都冇出現過<br />\n點解個個都可以將(假公平)一直傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港為例<br />\n窮嘅新移民可以攞到好多褔利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗點做野就可以同有志氣，唔攞褔利嘅人一樣嘅生活質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢地黎得最高物價指數嘅香港,冇能力就要捱苦,合情合理,但係現實就係咁撚唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學生又係,你上一代嘅唔努力,就代表你嘅資源係要少啲<br />\n但係又唔撚係,窮嘅參加好多野都唔洗錢,反而冇咁窮嘅就冇機會或唔想用多餘錢參加活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 香港褔利政策同埋啲社工好撚野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68da45b37f5e51c18fcb969d5fcc6e31e5aca69","tid":832165,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"仲有表面上最公平嘅運動"},{"pid":"795288c592e86efd06a23fdadfc812d8e7a20fd2","tid":832165,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:57:12.000Z","msg":"每個人嘅天資都唔同,部份人唔洗點練就好勁<br />\n而運動只係係同一個規則下比賽,根本冇衡量運動員背後付出嘅時間同埋努力,其實都唔可以算係 (等價交換)下嘅公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efded8459a0dc0542f0a58144d54f681b9d65602","tid":832165,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"所以根本就唔存在公平，所有野都係假公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d590c60e87cd10ed89b55132ee85e91a20295a2","tid":832165,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:01:48.000Z"